## API Version
* /conm/v1

## Metadata Content [/]

___
***Table Routes:***
| URL                     | Method | INFO                              |
| ----------------------- | ------ | ----------------------------------|
| `/`                     | GET    | Get All Metadata                  |
| `/{id}`                 | GET    | Get Metadata By Id                |
| `/store`                | POST   | Save Metadata                     |
| `/delete/{id}`          | GET    | Delete Metadata                   |
| `/update/{id}`          | POST   | Update Metadata By Id             |
| `/download/{id}`        | GET    | increase Number Of video Download |
| `/share/{id}`           | GET    | increase Number Of video Share    |
| `/view/{id}`            | GET    | increase Number Of video View     |
| `/save/{id}`            | GET    | increase Number Of video Save     |

___
**Save Metadata Parameter:**
| Parameter           | type   | Status   | Description                   |
| --------------------| ------ | -------- | ------------------------------|
| `user_id`           | uuid   | required | User ID                       |
| `video_title`       | string | required | Title of Video                |
| `video_description` | string | required | Description of Video          |
| `video_genre`       | string | required | Genre of Video                |
| `privacy`           | string | required | privacy video(public/private) |

___
**Update Metadata By Id:**
| Parameter           | type   | Status   | Description                   |
| --------------------| ------ | -------- | ------------------------------|
| `video_title`       | string | optimal  | Title of Video                |
| `video_description` | string | optimal  | Description of Video          |
| `video_genre`       | string | optimal  | Genre of Video                |
| `privacy`           | string | optimal  | privacy video(public/private) |

___
