## Content Categoritation [/category]

___
***Table Routes:***
| URL                     | Method | INFO                            | 
| ----------------------- | ------ | --------------------------------|
| `/{id}`                 | GET    | Get Metadata By category_id     |
| `/search`               | POST   | Search metadata By category_id  |
| `/add`                  | POST   | Add category_id In metadata     |
| `/remove`               | POST   | Delete category_id In metadata  |

___
* Search Metadata By category_id parameter
    * Single Query : `just use title/genre parameter`
    * Multi Query : `use title and genre parameter`

**Search Parameter:**
| Parameter           | type   | Status   | Description                   |
| --------------------| ------ | -------- | ------------------------------|
| `title`             | string | optimal  | Title of Video                |
| `genre`             | string | optimal  | Genre of Video                |
| `category_id`       | string | required | Genre of Video                |

___
**Add And Remove Category Parameter:**
| Parameter           | type   | Status   | Description                   |
| --------------------| ------ | -------- | ------------------------------|
| `metadata_id`       | uuid   | required | User ID                       |
| `category`          | string | required | category_id of Video          |

